{
  "stem": "7832.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A [NON-ENGLISH] means a gofer And I was picking up papers from the SS, taking them down the-- the road to be signed for zahlappell for the block elders [INAUDIBLE] and take them back.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After that, I was standing guard by the gate to let work men in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After the SS let them in, I was to report whoever was coming in like electrician or a plumber or somebody that delivered something to report them to the SS, sign them in for how much time and all that, and then-- you know, so-- and I did that one day.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this boy came through.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I never saw-- the whole day, all I saw people coming through is like-- not very many came.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One-- one man came and was carrying a package with a green insignia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Another one came with a purple one.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "These were all PLOs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Like, you know, they were in the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were prisoners of war for different reasons-- political.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so-- and he was the only one with the Jewish star.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I said, oh my God.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "A Jew-- I haven't seen a Jewish boy around for so long.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And but he came up to me and he told me what he was doing, he says, I'm a plumber and I will be here.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I'm supposed to be here for an hour to fix something by the SS office, so, you know, quarters.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he says-- and he saw my-- he knew I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he says, I work in the-- real fast-- I work in the Sonderkommando.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one of my sisters, my only sister that's left alive in this camp, gave me extra time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I says, I don't want to see your face.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
